Revision:
  716

Changes:
- Identifies *.fos files as AngelScript sources.
- Slightly modified parser which supports some AngelScript features:
  - Recoginizes handles (@, @+) and its combinitions with & and [] in types,
  - all class members are public,
- Command @weight <number> added. Use it with @name command to declare member groups weight,
  which is used:
  - If SORT_BRIEF_DOCS option is enabled then member groups are sorted by weight
    (in descending order). Group members sorted by names. Groups which have one weight
    sorted by first member name as in the original doxygen.
  - Attribute weight added to sectiondef element in the doxygen xml output.
  - Default weight: 100
- OPTIMIZE_FOR_FONLINE option. Forces to insert spaces after AS handlers and pointers,
  not before.
- TOC_ADD_* options. Allow to specify which types of member groups will be included in
  the expanded index (see TOC_EXPAND option).
  
